                <h1>What’s the Cost of a Level 2 Background Check?</h1>
                <p>A level 2 background check typically costs between $50 to $100, depending on the provider and the specific checks included, such as criminal history and fingerprinting. This check is often required for positions involving direct contact with vulnerable populations or sensitive information, ensuring thorough vetting for safety.</p>
